<h2 class="main-title">Reviyou App</h2>
New mobile app allows you to exchange votes and feedback on the professional skills and performance of anybody.

It could be a celebrity you enjoy seeking on TV from you couch at home or your favorite professor at college or just you colleague or boss at work!

<img class="alignright size-full wp-image-5184" alt="" src="http://reviyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/bubbles1.png" width="455" height="129" />


[fusion_text]<img class="alignright size-full wp-image-5187" alt="" src="http://reviyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/right.png" width="348" height="665" />
<h2 class="main-title">Multi device support, no registration</h2>
Works with most of android\ios based devices.

Use any Facebook gmail or twitter account to login.

We only use your info to identify you as a Reviyou user and it's not available for others. The only exception is when you leave a feedback - we show just your first and last name.
<img class="size-full wp-image-5192 alignleft" alt="" src="http://reviyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/devices.png" width="381" height="160" />


<h2 class="main-title" style="margin-top: 20px;"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-5206" alt="" src="http://reviyou.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/iphone-6.png" width="228" height="688" />3 easy steps to use Reviyou app:</h2>
<h3>1. See the most popular profiles</h3>
Browse what most of the people find interesting or search for anybody specific!
<h3>2. Create profile if it doesn't exist yet</h3>
Create a profile, it would be available for everyone, send a link to your friends!
<h3>3. Vote and Engage</h3>
Voting is easy and fun. You can also leave a feedback or read what other people think.